snippet: The police cordoned off the historic central building on the Princeton University campus in New Jersey for a few  hours Tuesday night after someone reported gunshots.
abstract: Report of gunshots prompts police to cordon off historic central building on Princeton University campus in New Jersey for about three hours; Princeton police find nothing after searching building.
lead_paragraph: The police cordoned off the historic central building on the Princeton University campus in New Jersey for a few  hours Tuesday night after someone reported gunshots.

headline.main: Gunfire Report Closes a Princeton Hall
